Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到艦橋去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙
